---
title: BBQ Beef Bowls Rice, Cucumber Salad, White Cheddar & BBQ Mayo
description: Prep, sizzle, zap, serve–that’s the sound of our Fast & Fresh weeknight wonder meal! Thanks to a few clever time-savers from our chefs, you’ll be savoring a satisfying rice bowl topped with BBQ-sauced ground beef, peppers, and onions in 15 minutes—no joke! Top your bowls with fresh tomato-cucumber salad and sprinkle with white cheddar cheese, then dollop with sour cream, drizzle with BBQ mayo, and finish with chopped cilantro and a bright squeeze of fresh lime juice.
